Tags:
  - Discernment-Truth=Knowledge=The Excellence of Wisdom
By: Thomas Traherne
---
Though a weak Christian may believe great things by an implicit faith, yet it
is very desirable his faith should be turned into assurance, and that cannot be
but by the riches of knowledge and understanding.
